curam.omega3.request
Class ParameterTypeRegistry

java.lang.Object
  curam.omega3.request.ParameterTypeRegistry

public final class ParameterTypeRegistry
extends java.lang.Object

This class maintains a list of the parameter name prefixes and the type of item associated with that prefix. Any new prefix constant should be defined here and not in a custom tag class. Prefixes or other constants that are not used to associate a parameter type with a request item should not be declared here.

PREFIX_RETURN_PAGE

public static final java.lang.String PREFIX_RETURN_PAGE
This is the name used for the request parameter which contains the URL of the page to return to if there is a validation error. It is added automatically as a hidden field by the display form tag.
